---
// Permit Service Teaser - Professional contractor version
---

<div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 p-8">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="border-b-4 border-cyan-500 pb-4 mb-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">
        Complete Permit & Engineering Service
      </h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">
        Full-service permit handling and technical documentation for all waterproofing projects
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 border-2 border-slate-100">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">Technical Documentation</h4>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-slate-100">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">CAD Site Plans</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">INCLUDED</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-slate-100">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Structural Cross-Sections</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">INCLUDED</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-slate-100">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Engineer Stamps (P.Eng)</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">INCLUDED</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">As-Built Drawings</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">INCLUDED</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 border-2 border-slate-100">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">Permit Management</h4>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-slate-100">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Building Permit Application</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">2-3 DAYS</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-slate-100">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Code Compliance Review</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">100%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-slate-100">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Inspection Scheduling</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">WE HANDLE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">Permit Fees</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">TRANSPARENT</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-amber-50 border-2 border-yellow-300 p-4 mb-6">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        <span class="font-bold uppercase">No Delays:</span> Our in-house engineering team ensures fast permit approval. 
        All drawings meet Ontario Building Code requirements. Licensed engineers on staff.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
      <a href="/services/permits" class="bg-navy-900 text-white px-6 py-3 text-center font-bold hover:bg-navy-900 transition-colors uppercase">
        Learn About Our Process
      </a>
      <a href="tel:437-545-0067" class="bg-amber-500 text-black px-6 py-3 text-center font-bold hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors uppercase">
        Get Free Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>